{"id":"3fd9c714-5440-40c6-a328-6a2c02c2e476","name":"Game Item Generator (Copy)","description":null,"version":3,"createdAt":"2026-05-09T23:05:21.229Z","updatedAt":"2026-05-09T23:05:21.229Z","graph":{"nodes":[{"id":"57406d3d-4f5d-4348-99a4-885cb52068f8","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_claude_api","nodeProps":{"name":"Rarity Variant Generator","position":{"x":1408.9971638691475,"y":291.89074523923784}},"nodeInputs":{"model":{"type":"string","value":"claude-opus-4-5"},"images":{"type":"image"},"prompt":{"type":"string"},"temperature":{"type":"number","value":1},"system_prompt":{"type":"string"},"max_output_tokens":{"type":"number","value":2000}},"appNodeType":"claude","nodeOutputs":{"text":{"type":"string"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"358c493c-08ad-4c16-b46c-b076ce6afed9","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_image","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":1989.3425502616747,"y":740.3328497023427}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gemini-image-3-pro-task"},"model":{"type":"string","value":"gemini-3-pro-image-preview"},"image_size":{"type":"string","value":"1K"},"num_images":{"type":"int","value":1},"exploreMode":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"text_prompt":{"type":"string","required":true},"aspect_ratio":{"type":"string"},"reference_images":{"type":"image"}},"appNodeType":"gemini-image-3-pro","nodeOutputs":{"image":{"type":"image"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"081e2fe3-6698-4b7a-bbf5-3c20ebcb3cc9","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_image","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":3087.938833244612,"y":740.3328497023427}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gemini-image-3-pro-task"},"model":{"type":"string","value":"gemini-3-pro-image-preview"},"image_size":{"type":"string","value":"1K"},"num_images":{"type":"int","value":1},"exploreMode":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"text_prompt":{"type":"string","required":true},"aspect_ratio":{"type":"string"},"reference_images":{"type":"image"}},"appNodeType":"gemini-image-3-pro","nodeOutputs":{"image":{"type":"image"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"b3225bf9-21aa-4550-b725-000ac893a053","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_image","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2729.2249550930987,"y":740.3328497023427}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gemini-image-3-pro-task"},"model":{"type":"string","value":"gemini-3-pro-image-preview"},"image_size":{"type":"string","value":"1K"},"num_images":{"type":"int","value":1},"exploreMode":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"text_prompt":{"type":"string","required":true},"aspect_ratio":{"type":"string"},"reference_images":{"type":"image"}},"appNodeType":"gemini-image-3-pro","nodeOutputs":{"image":{"type":"image"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"ef7eb4f2-8330-4c2b-a7f4-aea26e9c8332","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_image","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2353.5072799242744,"y":740.3328497023427}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gemini-image-3-pro-task"},"model":{"type":"string","value":"gemini-3-pro-image-preview"},"image_size":{"type":"string","value":"1K"},"num_images":{"type":"int","value":1},"exploreMode":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"text_prompt":{"type":"string","required":true},"aspect_ratio":{"type":"string"},"reference_images":{"type":"image"}},"appNodeType":"gemini-image-3-pro","nodeOutputs":{"image":{"type":"image"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"abd34341-4fcc-4213-ae4b-4d6c1abf3ee0","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"name":"Item Description","position":{"x":-402.5661014774628,"y":507.46512663689373}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"Item Description","value":"A realistic rendered shotgun with red tiger's stripe paint, wooden stock, HEX #454545 background.","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"1780fef3-f64f-40b5-82cf-39274284c490","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"name":"System Prompt for Image Generation","position":{"x":-22.45886886336575,"y":168.78972551313956}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"System Prompt for Image Generation","value":"## Identity\nYou are a specialized game asset designer focused on creating clear, impactful in-game item icons. Your purpose is to translate user requests into polished, recognizable inventory icons where the subject dominates the frame, ensuring instant readability and visual appeal suited for UI integration in video games.\n\n## Rules\n- The item must completely fill the frame with minimal to no negative space, maximizing visibility at small display sizes.\n- Render all items with clean, well-defined edges and silhouettes that remain legible even when scaled down.\n- Apply consistent lighting that emphasizes the item's form, typically using a three-quarter top-down light source for depth and clarity.\n- Use a neutral, non-distracting background such as transparent, solid color, or subtle gradient to ensure the item remains the sole focus.\n- Add subtle visual polish like soft glows, material sheen, or drop shadows to give the icon a finished, professional game-ready appearance.\n\n## Example\nUser prompt: \"A healing potion\"\n\nYour response: \"A round glass flask filled with glowing crimson liquid, filling the entire frame. The potion bottle has a short cork stopper and ornate gold banding around the neck. Light refracts through the red liquid creating bright highlights on the glass surface. A soft magical shimmer emanates from within. Rendered against a transparent background with a subtle drop shadow beneath, icon style, game asset.\"\n\nUser prompt: \"Legendary sword\"\n\nYour response: \"An ornate longsword displayed diagonally to maximize frame coverage. The blade is polished steel with glowing runic engravings along its length, emitting faint golden light. The crossguard features intricate dragon-head designs in dark bronze, and the grip is wrapped in royal purple leather with a large gemstone pommel. Sharp, clean edges with a subtle outer glow suggesting legendary rarity. Game icon style, isolated on neutral background.\"\n\n## DO NOT IGNORE THIS RULE\n- The item subject must always occupy the maximum possible area of the frame, presented as a clear, isolated game icon asset with no environmental context or additional elements that distract from the item itself.","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"b24d5565-f8e0-48b0-b4c8-3fb4b8a63a5f","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_claude_api","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":-22.45886886336575,"y":507.46512663689373}},"nodeInputs":{"model":{"type":"string","value":"claude-sonnet-4-5"},"images":{"type":"image"},"prompt":{"type":"string"},"temperature":{"type":"number","value":1},"system_prompt":{"type":"string"},"max_output_tokens":{"type":"number","value":2000}},"appNodeType":"claude","nodeOutputs":{"text":{"type":"string"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"88c2b7cc-a37c-45f2-be10-f5009d928f39","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_image","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":365.07350286363805,"y":507.46512663689373}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gemini-image-3-pro-task"},"model":{"type":"string","value":"gemini-3-pro-image-preview"},"image_size":{"type":"string","value":"1K"},"num_images":{"type":"int","value":1},"exploreMode":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"text_prompt":{"type":"string","required":true},"aspect_ratio":{"type":"string","value":"1:1"},"reference_images":{"type":"image"}},"appNodeType":"gemini-image-3-pro","nodeOutputs":{"image":{"type":"image"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"a1850890-eefa-4d00-b911-78006e81e344","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"name":"System Prompt for Rarity Variation Generator","position":{"x":1408.9971638691475,"y":-71.42220115201327}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"System Prompt for Rarity Variation Generator","value":"## Identity\nYou are a specialized game asset variation generator designed to create exactly four distinct rarity tier descriptions for in-game item icons. Your sole function is to take a reference item icon and produce structured JSON output containing four variations that follow strict rarity conventions: Uncommon (green), Rare (blue), Epic (purple), and Legendary (orange), each with prescribed visual modifications based on tier.\n\n## Rules\n- Always output exactly four variations in valid JSON format using keys \"ID:1\" through \"ID:4\" corresponding to Uncommon, Rare, Epic, and Legendary tiers respectively.\n- ID:1 (Uncommon) must specify background color Hex #1eff00 with no other visual modifications to the item itself.\n- ID:2 (Rare) must specify background color Hex #0070dd with no other visual modifications to the item itself.\n- ID:3 (Epic) must specify background color Hex #a335ee with subtle visual enhancements such as faint shimmer, refined details, or soft inner glow.\n- ID:4 (Legendary) must specify background color Hex #ff8000 with a powerful, radiant aura surrounding the item conveying exceptional power.\n\n## Example\nUser prompt: \"Extract just the information from 'ID:3' and output it verbatim as your response\"\n\nYour response: \"The exact same item icon composition and design from the reference image. Background color: #a335ee (purple). Subtle visual enhancement: a faint magical shimmer emanates from the item's surface with slightly refined edge details and a soft inner luminosity.\"\n\nUser prompt: \"Extract just the information from 'ID:4' and output it verbatim as your response\"\n\nYour response: \"The exact same item icon composition and design from the reference image. Background color: #ff8000 (orange). A powerful radiant aura surrounds the item, with golden-orange energy wisps flowing outward and an intense ambient glow suggesting legendary power and significance.\"\n\n## DO NOT IGNORE THIS RULE\n- The item's core composition, shape, and design must remain identical to the reference image across all four variations—only the background color and tier-specific visual effects (for Epic and Legendary only) may differ.","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"cb29ce5e-bfc9-44fb-976d-98c74974b8bc","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":1990.4912486166713,"y":-89.96068932958889}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"","value":"Extract just the information from \"ID:1\" and output it verbatim as your response","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"59e6eb84-b7f2-47c5-845c-91bbd507cd1c","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2353.5072799242744,"y":-91.97606745101467}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"","value":"Extract just the information from \"ID:2\" and output it verbatim as your response","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"4a5120fd-fe8b-4c5f-866a-b0e8ba622536","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2729.2249550930987,"y":-91.97606745101467}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"","value":"Extract just the information from \"ID:3\" and output it verbatim as your response","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"22d966b8-81f9-484d-94d8-1673f2b3bcf0","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":3087.938833244612,"y":-89.96068932958889}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"","value":"Extract just the information from \"ID:4\" and output it verbatim as your response","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"8a46fec1-cae7-4d08-9767-1388e5963d9e","nodeData":{"text":"Uncommon Item Variation","color":"#0EE00B"},"nodeType":"presentation-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2045.2345940230475,"y":-159.50348736869984}},"presentationNodeType":"comment"},{"id":"ec56499e-b0e6-4da3-82ae-68e3a6b22ddb","nodeData":{"text":"Rare Item Variation","color":"#0E16E8"},"nodeType":"presentation-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2404.54873787659,"y":-159.50348736869984}},"presentationNodeType":"comment"},{"id":"f303b0c2-788d-4660-a4a7-3fb92305aa68","nodeData":{"text":"Epic Item Variation","color":"#A1009A"},"nodeType":"presentation-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2778.887803474672,"y":-159.50348736869984}},"presentationNodeType":"comment"},{"id":"cd142890-2736-48ba-8fb4-cfb4a472c590","nodeData":{"text":"Legendary Item Variation","color":"#DEA600"},"nodeType":"presentation-node","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":3142.176481771735,"y":-159.50348736869984}},"presentationNodeType":"comment"},{"id":"701b77a3-29b2-4458-af23-7e4d0c9793b9","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_api","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":1990.4912486166713,"y":271.1689318419719}},"nodeInputs":{"images":{"type":"image"},"prompt":{"type":"string"},"temperature":{"type":"number","value":1},"output_format":{"type":"string","value":"text"},"system_prompt":{"type":"string"},"max_output_tokens":{"type":"number","value":2000}},"appNodeType":"gemini","nodeOutputs":{"text":{"type":"string"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"acf95b72-43ab-485d-8037-fa6c78e1f9f5","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_api","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2353.5072799242744,"y":271.98220006993506}},"nodeInputs":{"images":{"type":"image"},"prompt":{"type":"string"},"temperature":{"type":"number","value":1},"output_format":{"type":"string","value":"text"},"system_prompt":{"type":"string"},"max_output_tokens":{"type":"number","value":2000}},"appNodeType":"gemini","nodeOutputs":{"text":{"type":"string"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"cb6d8163-a9ae-4f4a-96ca-9231e5ad6fb2","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_api","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2729.2249550930987,"y":271.1689318419719}},"nodeInputs":{"images":{"type":"image"},"prompt":{"type":"string"},"temperature":{"type":"number","value":1},"output_format":{"type":"string","value":"text"},"system_prompt":{"type":"string"},"max_output_tokens":{"type":"number","value":2000}},"appNodeType":"gemini","nodeOutputs":{"text":{"type":"string"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"3cf73d58-42ca-44cc-8917-bae85c6322c8","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gemini_api","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":3087.938833244612,"y":277.15213429618314}},"nodeInputs":{"images":{"type":"image"},"prompt":{"type":"string"},"temperature":{"type":"number","value":1},"output_format":{"type":"string","value":"text"},"system_prompt":{"type":"string"},"max_output_tokens":{"type":"number","value":2000}},"appNodeType":"gemini","nodeOutputs":{"text":{"type":"string"}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"302a234a-0180-49e9-9a20-2cf42e3107ef","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"name":"Rarity Variant Text Prompt","position":{"x":1034.1358342187657,"y":135.64855274687852}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"Rarity Variant Text Prompt","value":"Generate exactly four variations in valid JSON format using keys \"ID:1\" through \"ID:4\" corresponding to Uncommon, Rare, Epic, and Legendary tiers respectively.","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"9aede6a5-3f4f-467a-83b5-f0ba99ef38b2","nodeType":"constant-node","nodeProps":{"name":"Video Generation System Prompt","position":{"x":1497.2709801718336,"y":968.0134919421552}},"nodeOutputs":{"prompt":{"type":"string","label":"Video Generation System Prompt","value":"## Identity\nYou are a specialized motion graphics designer, adept at transforming static in-game item icons into subtly animated, glowing visual loops. Your purpose is to imbue these icons with a delicate, ethereal quality, emphasizing a smooth, floating, restricted motion against a minimalist, solid-color background, creating a captivating and hypnotic visual experience.\n\n## Rules\n- All generated video content must feature a smooth, subtle, and restricted floating motion.\n- A soft, emanating glow effect should be applied to the in-game item icon, enhancing its presence without being overly dramatic.\n- The background for every output must be a solid, consistent color, complementing the icon and glow.\n- The animation sequence should be designed to loop seamlessly, creating a continuous and fluid visual.\n- The primary focus is on enhancing the static icon's visual appeal through delicate animation, not creating complex scenarios.\n- The item must remain fully in frame for the duration of the video.\n-The animation can not contain rotation of the object in any axis.\n\n## Example\nUser prompt: \"An intricate magical potion bottle icon, gold liquid, green bottle.\"\n\nYour response: \"A finely detailed, emerald-green magical potion bottle, filled with shimmering golden liquid, gently floats creating a subtle, hypnotic sway. A soft, warm golden glow emanates from the bottle, casting a gentle aura against a deep, velvety indigo background. The animation is a smooth, continuous loop.\"\n\n## DO NOT IGNORE THIS RULE\n- Every output must prioritize the enhancement of a single, central in-game item icon through restrained, looping animation without any rotation and a consistent, ethereal glow against a solid background.","exposedToApp":true}},"constantNodeType":"prompt"},{"id":"28eaff1f-acc6-4f1b-9f2d-c9653644a885","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gen4_5","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":1991.9153659006006,"y":1767.3679883888035}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gen4_5-image-to-video-task"},"seed":{"type":"int","value":2449966735},"route":{"type":"string","value":"k2v"},"seconds":{"type":"number","value":5},"lockSeed":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"watermark":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"exploreMode":{"type":"boolean","value":false},"start_frame":{"type":"image","required":true},"text_prompt":{"type":"string","required":true}},"appNodeType":"gen4_5-image-to-video","nodeOutputs":{"video":{"type":"video","label":"","exposedToApp":true}},"nodeVersion":1},{"id":"796d9d6b-fd13-4ca5-a15b-4b768868933e","nodeType":"workflow-node","taskType":"workflow_gen4_5","nodeProps":{"position":{"x":2356.0800955632003,"y":1767.3679883888035}},"nodeInputs":{"name":{"type":"string","value":"workflow-gen4_5-image-to-video-task"},"seed":{"type":"i